      "content": "the hotlines dont really help with this kind of thing. it's not like i'm in a panic or anything, i'm just... hollow. it's like the light just went out and it's never coming back. i look at my life and i just see a void. how am i supposed to keep going when there's literally nothing left to move toward?",
